    ‚àá r‚ÜêE ReplyMail ToTitBody_Html_bcc;h;mid;hdr
      ‚çù Like SendMail but automatically sets In-Reply-To from the event's Message-ID header
      :Access public
      h‚Üê‚ÜëE.headers
      mid‚Üê‚äÉ(h‚ç™‚äÇ'')[(h[;1]‚ç≥‚äÇ'Message-ID');2]
      hdr‚Üê(0<‚â¢mid)/'In-Reply-To'mid   ‚çù empty if no Message-ID found
      r‚Üêhdr SendMail ToTitBody_Html_bcc
